the Grand Master. Great Architect of Nature, help me to find the
true path out of the labyrinth of lies!

   After this, three pages were left blank in the diary, and then
the following was written:

  I have had a long and instructive talk alone with Brother V., who
advised me to hold fast by brother A. Though I am unworthy, much was
revealed to me. Adonai is the name of the creator of the world. Elohim
